'''伏尔加广播电台'''（{{lang-ru|Радио Волга}}；{{lang-de|Radio Wolga}}）是一家面向驻[[东德|东德]]及[[捷克斯洛伐克|捷克斯洛伐克]][[苏军|苏军]]进行广播的电台，节目以[[俄语|俄语]]为主<ref>[https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=djFiAAAAMAAJ&q=%22Radio+Volga%22+gdr&dq=%22Radio+Volga%22+gdr&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwio_4LD4KfLAhUHyRQKHTUBCigQ6AEIMDAA ''The Mass Media of the German-speaking Countries''] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=djFiAAAAMAAJ&q=%22Radio+Volga%22+gdr&dq=%22Radio+Volga%22+gdr&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwio_4LD4KfLAhUHyRQKHTUBCigQ6AEIMDAA |date=20200131154843 }}, John Sandford, Oswald Wolff, 1976</ref>。

==概要==
伏尔加广播电台总部位于[[德意志民主共和国|德意志民主共和国]][[波茨坦|波茨坦]]，1945年7月1日开始播音。电台通过[[柏林|柏林]]附近的{{le|Königs Wusterhausen长波发射台|Königs Wusterhausen radio transmitter}}和[[马格德堡|马格德堡]]附近的{{le|Burg中波发射台|Burg AM transmitter}}向驻守东德以及捷克斯洛伐克的苏军进行广播<ref name ="WRTH">[https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=ENI6AAAAIAAJ&q=%22Radio+Volga%22++K%C3%B6nigs+Wusterhausen&dq=%22Radio+Volga%22++K%C3%B6nigs+Wusterhausen&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjSxuuG4qfLAhWFuRQKHUD5Cw8Q6AEILTAA ''World Radio TV Handbook''] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=ENI6AAAAIAAJ&q=%22Radio+Volga%22++K%C3%B6nigs+Wusterhausen&dq=%22Radio+Volga%22++K%C3%B6nigs+Wusterhausen&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjSxuuG4qfLAhWFuRQKHUD5Cw8Q6AEILTAA |date=20200131154955 }}, Oluf Lund-Johansen Cardfont Publishers under license from Billboard Publications, 1974, page 70</ref>，使用[[长波|长波]]261[[kHz|kHz]]和[[中波|中波]]1323kHz播出。除了对驻外苏军广播，该台还会转播[[莫斯科广播电台|莫斯科广播电台]]的[[德语|德语]]节目。1990年[[两德统一|两德统一]]后，该台开始向一些被称为“{{link-de|Radioropa|Radioropa}}”的私营广播电台出租长波频率的播出时段<ref>[https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=KXxJzHGJas0C&lpg=PA40&dq=%22FFB%22%20Radio%20%22Berlin%22%20%221994%22&pg=PA41#v=onepage&q=%22FFB%22%20Radio%20%22Berlin%22%20%221994%22&f=true ''Radiogeschichten: Zeitreise und Exkursionen in die Berliner RadioWelten''] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=KXxJzHGJas0C&lpg=PA40&dq=%22FFB%22%20Radio%20%22Berlin%22%20%221994%22&pg=PA41#v=onepage&q=%22FFB%22%20Radio%20%22Berlin%22%20%221994%22&f=true |date=20200131154638 }}, Die Radionauten, BoD, 2005, page 41</ref>。另外，该台也向东德转播[[苏联中央电视台|苏联中央电视台]]{{le|第一套节目|Programme One}}<ref>[https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=jMdNAAAAYAAJ&dq=soviet+television+TSS+Berlin&focus=searchwithinvolume&q=TSS-1+ ''World Radio TV Handbook''] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=jMdNAAAAYAAJ&dq=soviet+television+TSS+Berlin&focus=searchwithinvolume&q=TSS-1+ |date=20200131154825 }}, Volume 39, Billboard Publications, 1984, page 398</ref>。

1994年，随着[[俄军|俄军]]撤出德国，伏尔加广播电台停播，其频率被德国的一些“Radioropa”电台接管，直至2000年底“Radioropa”电台执照全部到期为止<ref>[https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=qTUqAQAAIAAJ&q=Radioropa+Info&dq=Radioropa+Info&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj2s6bR56fLAhVJ8RQKHaaIA9EQ6AEILjAD ''World Radio TV Handbook''] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=qTUqAQAAIAAJ&q=Radioropa+Info&dq=Radioropa+Info&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj2s6bR56fLAhVJ8RQKHaaIA9EQ6AEILjAD |date=20200131160224 }}, Volume 51,Cardfont Publishers under license from Billboard Publications., 1997, page 88</ref>。

